<eps file="stop.eps" height="4cm">
<img src="stop.png">
</figure>
<figure loc="here">
<eps file="stop.eps" height="4cm">
<img src="stop.png">
<caption><bf>NOTE</bf>: The ATI All-in-Wonder cards (which are not the same
as the ATI TV Wonder, TV Wonder VE or TV Wonder Pro) <em>will not</em> work
