If you are in North America you will use the DataDirect
grabber which is built-in to MythTV.  You <em>do not</em> need to install
XMLTV, but you need <bf>wget</bf> version 1.9.1 or higher.

Get XMLTV from <url url="http://xmltv.sourceforge.net"
name="http://xmltv.sourceforge.net">.  Download the latest version (0.5.38).

<code>
NOTE for Mandrake users:  If you have added a "PLF" mirror, you may skip the
next step and type:

# urpmi libmp3lame0 libmp3lame0-devel

